com.streambase.sbunit.ext

Interface TupleMatcher

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AllTupleMatcher, AnythingMatcher, AnyTupleMatcher, FieldBasedTupleMatcher, NothingMatcher, NotTupleMatcher

    public interface TupleMatcher
    TupleMatchers are used by StreamMatcher to determine if a tuple matches as an expected tuple or is an unexpected tuple.
